There are three ways to keep up to date about the changes with Sh:

1- Visit the homepage at:
   http://www.libsh.org/

2- Add this RSS feed to your RSS newsreader:
   http://sourceforge.net/export/rss2_projnews.php?group_id=85632&rss_fulltext=1

3- Subscribe to the announce mailing list:
   http://lists.libsh.org/cgi-bin/mailman/listinfo/libsh-announce
